# /services — Core business logic layer
# Services are called by controllers and orchestrate models, external APIs,
# and domain rules. They are framework-agnostic and independently testable.
# Examples:
#   authService.js      → Password hashing, JWT generation, token verification
#   userService.js      → User CRUD, avatar upload processing
#   emissionService.js  → Emission calculations, aggregation, trend analysis
#   reportService.js    → Report generation, PDF/CSV export logic
#   emailService.js     → Transactional email dispatch (welcome, reset password)
